'''天主教里斯本宗主教區'''（{{lang-la|Patriarchatus Lisbonensis}}；{{lang-pt|Patriarcado de Lisboa}}）是[[羅馬天主教會|羅馬天主教會]]以[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]首都[[里斯本|里斯本]]為中心的一個{{link-en|宗主教區|Patriarchate}}，下轄七個教區。

宗主教區於2011年時有1,870,000名教友（佔轄區總人口83.6%），有284個[[堂區|堂區]]、566名[[司鐸|司鐸]]、84名終身執事、387名修士和1,092名修女。現任宗主教為[[厄瑪奴耳·克萊門特|厄瑪奴耳三世]][[樞機|樞機]]<ref>{{cite web |title=CLEMENTE Card. Manuel |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_clemente_m.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-04-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420131427/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_clemente_m.html |archivedate=2019-04-20 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-pt|若亞敬·奧斯定·達-西爾瓦-門德斯|Joaquim Augusto da Silva Mendes}}、{{link-pt|但尼爾·巴塔爾阿-恩里克斯|Daniel Batalha Henriques}}和{{link-pt|阿梅里科·厄瑪奴耳·阿爾韋斯-阿吉阿爾|Américo Manuel Alves Aguiar}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 31.01.2008 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/01/31/0067/00158.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-05-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525142500/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2008/01/31/0067/00158.html |archivedate=2020-05-25 |language=it |date=2008-01-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 13.10.2018 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/10/13/181013b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-05-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200525142734/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2018/10/13/181013b.html |archivedate=2020-05-25 |language=en |date=2018-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 01.03.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/03/01/190301b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-04-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420124758/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/03/01/190301b.html |archivedate=2019-04-20 |language=en |date=2019-03-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

4世紀升為教區，{{which|716年至1147年因[[摩爾人|摩爾人]]入侵而懸空}}。1394年升為總教區，1716年升為宗主教區。

